Welcome to Ambadi

A part of the renowned Murugappa Group, we the Ambadiâ€™s are one of India's biggest exporters of home linen and floor coverings, with a slew of awards and certifications to our credit. Our products are found on the shopping lists of premium linen brands and top notch international retailers. Our passion for the unusual and outstanding has led us to create the complete process chain to convent designs seamlessly from paper to product.



