About Us





Chairman’s Message


   As a successful and responsible entity, we invest into protection and development of nearby communities. With a ‘society first’ attitude, we unceasingly work towards the betterment of the communities wherein our operational presence exists. 






One Vision One Team


   We are a team of over 10,000 employees striving towards building a better India 






One Vision One Brand


   Our new visual identity is designed to help tell the story of integration in a simple and modern style. 




 
Since 1988, Adani Group, one of India's leading business houses with revenue of about $12 billion, has transformed into a global integrated infrastructure player in core industry verticals — resources, logistics and energy.







Businesses




											We are creating an internationally integrated infrastructure business and therefore commencing the most exciting phase of our development till now. This will encompass three equally vital components: resources, logistics & energy.
										

 







Sustainability





Environment


   With implementation of its green port ideology ensuring better environment control in desert conditions, the Adani Group company - APSEZ has been recognised internationally as the ‘World’s port for a better climate.’ 






Adani Foundation


   We live and work in nearby communities and take our societal commitments seriously. In India, we invest around three per cent of the group’s profits into community focused initiatives through the Adani Foundation. 






Safety


   As active members of the GSC, NSC, and the IFE – India, the group’s businesses offer independent advice, support and organise seminars that help towards introducing latest technologies and development in safety rules and regulations. 





 
Along with several proactive and protective initiatives, we have initiated numerous measures  to develop a sustainable eco-friendly business model. 







Investors




											Browse through this section to access in-depth financial figures, corporate governance reports and other related information regarding the listed Adani Group Companies.
										

 







Media





Media Release


   Browse through this section for the newest media releases related to Adani Group, or search through our exhaustive archives. 






Media Coverage


   News coverage for all Adani Group related companies accessible in chronological order or sort as per listed companies. 






Chairman's Corner


   "Our Business model is aligned with the national interest” read what Gautam Adani has to say about nation building. 






Media Library


   Our exhaustive library offers a repertoire of top-notch images, video footages and advertisements. 






Events


   Glance through most recent events organised for the environment, CSR, safety, and other causes that we remain committed towards. 






Social Media


   Connect with the latest happenings at Adani. Become a part of the conversation on our social media channels. 




 
Browse through this section for the most recent media releases and news on Adani group. Our exhaustive library offers a repertoire of top-notch images, video footages and advertisements.







Career





L & D


   We have developed superior people management systems and processes that help us meet aggressive commitments consistently. Our employees maintain competitive advantage through continuous learning & development thereby ensuring extraordinary results. 






Team Speaks


   You can listen to experienced professionals, graduates or even interns — the members of Adani Parivaar talking about life at Adani - who we are, what we do, and our journey of growth, scale and diversity. 






Team Connect


   We're a progressive group of people who believe in transforming the world for better and shall initiate a lot of new things together - festivals, happy hours, trips, workshops, games, lunch and a lot of fun. 





 
One Vision, One Team. Come and become an integral part of a team dedicated to nation building.
























