Home Page



	 

Madhya Bharat Agro products Ltd. (MBAPL) is one of the major private sector fertilizer manufacturer. MBAPL is dealing in manufacturing of BRP with installed production capacity of 99000 TPA (Licensed capacity -99000 TPA),best cartier replica SSP with installed capacity of 180000 TPY (Licensed capacity 240000 TPY) and Sulphuric Acid with installed capacity of 36000 TPY (having licensed capacity is 99000 TPY). Further the New Project GSSP (having licensed capacity is 180000 TPY) is underway making it completely integrated state of art manufacturing facility.

	Commercial production of BRP & Sulphuric Acid are an important milestone in the fast growth of company which is aimed to make its fertilizer unit self-sufficient in terms of major raw material input. Production of rock phosphate concentrate is an important achievement for the company as India heavily depends on the imports which render this material quite vulnerable to large fluctuations in quality and prices. Company commence production of SSP’s second major raw material i.e. Sulphuric Acid which is require raw material sulphur available at refinery near to unit, it make possible to manufacturing Sulphuric Acid at best economic and competitive cost. As company is only in country having independent/self-sufficient in both raw material of fertilizer with nearest and acute source.          

Omega Replica Watches is among the respected Swiss watch-making brands, identified using its unmatched horological accomplishments and temerarious innovative spirit.






 












 


